<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Acceso Denegado - Farmadescaso</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/colors.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/dashboard.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .access-denied-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: slideIn 0.5s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        .access-denied-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .access-denied-header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 0.5;
            }
            50% {
                transform: scale(1.1);
                opacity: 0.8;
            }
        }
        
        .access-denied-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            animation: shake 0.5s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            25% { transform: rotate(-10deg); }
            75% { transform: rotate(10deg); }
        }
        
        .access-denied-header h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .access-denied-body {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .access-denied-body h2 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .access-denied-body p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .access-denied-features {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .access-denied-features h3 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .feature-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .feature-item i {
            color: #28a745;
            margin-right: 12px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .btn-back {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 40px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        
        .btn-back:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.6);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-back:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        
        .decorative-elements {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .decorative-circle {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        .circle-1 {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            top: 10%;
            left: 10%;
            animation-delay: 0s;
        }
        
        .circle-2 {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            top: 60%;
            right: 10%;
            animation-delay: 2s;
        }
        
        .circle-3 {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            bottom: 10%;
            left: 20%;
            animation-delay: 4s;
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(180deg);
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .access-denied-container {
                margin: 20px;
            }
            
            .access-denied-header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .access-denied-icon {
                font-size: 60px;
            }
            
            .access-denied-header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .access-denied-body {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="access-denied-container">
        <div class="access-denied-header">
            <div class="decorative-elements">
                <div class="decorative-circle circle-1"></div>
                <div class="decorative-circle circle-2"></div>
                <div class="decorative-circle circle-3"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="access-denied-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
            </div>
            <h1>Acceso Denegado</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="access-denied-body">
            <h2>No tienes permisos para acceder a esta sección</h2>
            <p>
                Lo sentimos, pero esta área está reservada exclusivamente para administradores del sistema.
                Si crees que esto es un error, por favor contacta con el administrador.
            </p>
            
            <div class="access-denied-features">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Información</h3>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                    <span>Esta sección requiere permisos de administrador</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                    <span>Tu cuenta actual no tiene los permisos necesarios</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                    <span>Contacta con un administrador si necesitas acceso</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-back">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>
                Volver al Dashboard
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
